actions.name: AssociateServiceQuotaTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to associate the Service Quotas template with your organization

actions.name: DeleteServiceQuotaIncreaseRequestFromTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to remove the specified service quota from the service quota template

actions.name: DisassociateServiceQuotaTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to disassociate the Service Quotas template from your organization

actions.name: GetAWSDefaultServiceQuota
actions.description: Grants permission to return the details for the specified service quota, including the AWS default value

actions.name: GetAssociationForServiceQuotaTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to retrieve the ServiceQuotaTemplateAssociationStatus value, which tells you if the Service Quotas template is associated with an organization

actions.name: GetRequestedServiceQuotaChange
actions.description: Grants permission to retrieve the details for a particular service quota increase request

actions.name: GetServiceQuota
actions.description: Grants permission to return the details for the specified service quota, including the applied value

actions.name: GetServiceQuotaIncreaseRequestFromTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to retrieve the details for a service quota increase request from the service quota template

actions.name: ListAWSDefaultServiceQuotas
actions.description: Grants permission to list all default service quotas for the specified AWS service

actions.name: ListRequestedServiceQuotaChangeHistory
actions.description: Grants permission to request a list of the changes to quotas for a service

actions.name: ListRequestedServiceQuotaChangeHistoryByQuota
actions.description: Grants permission to request a list of the changes to specific service quotas

actions.name: ListServiceQuotaIncreaseRequestsInTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to return a list of the service quota increase requests from the service quota template

actions.name: ListServiceQuotas
actions.description: Grants permission to list all service quotas for the specified AWS service, in that account, in that Region

actions.name: ListServices
actions.description: Grants permission to list the AWS services available in Service Quotas

actions.name: ListTagsForResource
actions.description: Grants permission to view the existing tags on a SQ resource

actions.name: PutServiceQuotaIncreaseRequestIntoTemplate
actions.description: Grants permission to define and add a quota to the service quota template

actions.name: RequestServiceQuotaIncrease
actions.description: Grants permission to submit the request for a service quota increase

actions.name: TagResource
actions.description: Grants permission to associate a set of tags with an existing SQ resource

actions.name: UntagResource
actions.description: Grants permission to remove a set of tags from a SQ resource, where tags to be removed match a set of customer-supplied tag keys
